Youths in Bulagu village, Budalang&rsquo;i sub-location, Bunyala subcounty, have been urged to register for ID cards. They can go to the registrar of persons&rsquo; office every Tuesday to apply, village elder Marcela Taabu said.She spoke on Saturday at the burial of Clementina Auma, mother of Cornell Okumu, the chairman of Budalang&rsquo;i MP Ababu Namwamba&rsquo;s advisory committee.